title: Melvin Gordon ending holdout, Eagles-Packers TNF Preview (Football 9/26)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to react to the end of Melvin Gordon's holdout and what it means both for the Chargers right now and long-term (1:00). Then, the guys breakdown Thursday's matchup between the Eagles and Packers (11:00).
